    "headline": "Cadence Design Systems (NASDAQ:CDNS) Surprises With Q1 CY2026 Sales",
    "summary": "Electronic design automation company Cadence Design Systems (NASDAQ:CDNS) reported Q1 CY2026 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 18.7% year on year to $1.47 billion. The company’s full-year revenue guidance of $6.18 billion at the midpoint came in 0.7% above analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.96 per share was 4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
